{"tid":2403654,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【咁大件事無人講就我講啦！】食肆負責人必須安排所有員工每14天接受一次武肺病毒檢測","createTime":"2021-02-11T08:10:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-12T06:14:07.000Z","uid":257533,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"404d5f8c8ed3fac5571de428288c469d1130daae","tid":2403654,"uid":257533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T08:10:55.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">處所負責人必須安排所有員工每14天接受一次新冠病毒檢測，員工須保留有關檢測陰性結果供執法人員查核。</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">如場所負責人未有遵守相關規定，將被勒令停業3至14天不等，視乎違規情況可能引致的額外感染風險而定。此外，負責人仍最高可被判罰款五萬元和監禁六個月。</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">關於個app嘅討論，已經有好多啦！但關於<span class=\"red\">「強迫員工不斷檢測」</span>，似乎冇咩人講。<br />\n<br />\n可以點樣「配合」呀？</span><br />\n<br />\n而家除口罩食嘢嘅，又唔係我啲員工！你強迫戴口罩嘅人去檢測？你個腦都裝屎嘅！<br />\n<br />\n我啲員工檢測完，食客A一樣可以傳染食客B！但政府嘅做法，等於畀咗個「假安心」畀大家。仲危險過之前！<br />\n<br />\n集思廣益，求<span class=\"x-large\">好好配合</span>嘅方法！<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">有計出計，無計推po！</span></span>"},{"pid":"9f4bf0f77c4a1c78615adaa72474a65831f0c9ec","tid":2403654,"uid":257533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T08:14:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"65caf2b4cb767330c2ca63bd9ab6e95a5945fbf0","tid":2403654,"uid":257533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T08:14:31.000Z","msg":"推2"},{"pid":"92488e4540735da3bfd9b4ae8f27db17e552cfff","tid":2403654,"uid":257533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T08:14:42.000Z","msg":"推3推4"},{"pid":"5267a49520afaa982a919f9cb6121a516a1debe5","tid":2403654,"uid":257533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T08:14:53.000Z","msg":"推5"},{"pid":"c080eceb2e119e1c5555f09cf2108159ec0238c7","tid":2403654,"uid":257533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T08:15:04.000Z","msg":"推6"},{"pid":"911acdb268618664bddf1d801bbfd44f1fcb3b8b","tid":2403654,"uid":257533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply